            <p>Sega is hiring up for the Sonic Team, just as the series is celebrating its 35th anniversary.</p>
<p>As spotted by <a href="https://mynintendonews.com/2026/06/11/sega-is-heavily-recruiting-for-sonic-team/">My Nintendo News</a>, these roles include a few senior positions, including a producer, lead planner, lead graphics programmer, and a technical art manager.</p>

<figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Official Year Two Crossover Trailer | IGN Summer of Gaming 2026" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pnRThfS6iL0?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
